Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:27.26,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:29.05,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,...killed again, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:35.28,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(1158,493)}#07 Science Worship\NMisawa Cram School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:37.53,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:43.50,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,To think that a little reference textbook would cost as much as 3,600 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:44.40,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:49.05,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What could we have done with 3,600 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.67,0:00:51.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:52.96,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, To-u-ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:54.58,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What could we have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:56.96,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,All right, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.44,0:01:00.03,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If I had studied every day, I wouldn't have ended up in this-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:07.72,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:10.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.24,0:01:14.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Normal people don't eat 3,600 yen\Nworth of ice cream, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:17.25,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.25,0:01:21.31,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't let out a single word like\N"hot", "unpleasant", or "tired" at all, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.70,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Neither have I ever thought of using someone else's money,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:28.93,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,and in conclusion, I have never thought about wanting to eat ice cream at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:30.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:35.67,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Just say that you want to eat\Nsome ice cream in a store with air conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:39.80,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, this clothing is a materialization of The Lord's protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.19,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Never have I ever said that this was uncomfortable, hot,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.19,0:01:48.35,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,or wanted to try a "nuts, I can't even tell the difference between summer and winter clothing" experiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:48.35,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This very talkative sister and I have known each other for a while, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.26,0:01:51.06,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There's a reason why I say "it seems".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:54.39,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I don't possess any memories beyond two weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.49,0:02:00.78,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And, for another reason, I am keeping this from others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.82,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I especially don't want this sister to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:14.71,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Her tears and her smile were directed at me before I lost my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:18.93,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:20.65,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking away for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:23.35,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I am still in training,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.35,0:02:26.76,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,so I am forbidden from consuming any luxury foods!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:28.51,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we won't go for it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.51,0:02:30.85,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to force yourself to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.11,0:02:34.32,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,While I am indeed forbidden,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:36.67,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,as I am still a sister-in-training,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.67,0:02:41.09,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,it would be kind of difficult, kind of not difficult for me to have flawless conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.09,0:02:47.89,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, there could be a possibility that ice cream might accidentally fall into my mouth, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:53.94,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,A rather interesting negotiation you got going there, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.94,Default,blonde,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the lass, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:57.92,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.43,0:03:00.31,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,What, what's with your dull reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.98,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Your memories got blown away from all this heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:05.60,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:09.27,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Losing memories is a special privilege that belongs solely to mysterious, wave-emitting girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:12.29,Default,blonde,0000,0000,0000,,And, who is this miniature girl, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.15,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't tell me it's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:16.94,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,"Her" chest is a bit too flat for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:20.51,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, there are things you can and can't say...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she has a pedo body-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.65,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:33.04,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I am a sister affiliated with the English Purist Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:37.33,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Repent now, or forever hold your peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:47.30,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Shake! Shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.26,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Three shake drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.30,Default,blonde,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.56,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Letting you treat us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.60,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, it was all my treat in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.06,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Such misfortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:01.79,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:04.15,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you found a place in this crowd-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:09.93,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious-looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.10,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Way too suspicious-looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.41,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:17.75,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,"S-"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:19.04,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,"S-"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:20.28,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:22.67,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Spent all my money on food...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.50,Default,all,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.66,Default,all,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.66,0:04:28.68,Default,all,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.51,Default,both,0000,0000,0000,,All right!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.65,0:04:35.94,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, you said you spent all your money or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:40.63,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,The 100-yen hamburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:44.73,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I had a lot of coupons for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:49.15,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,...and so I went ahead and ordered thirty of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:52.23,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You got too much of a deal there, dumb girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.25,0:04:57.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:57.88,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I... umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.59,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Frustration meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.92,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Cost of train ticket home, 600 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:05.80,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.76,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Total assets, 500 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:10.58,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's the connection here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:12.40,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Spent too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:13.39,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,No planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.72,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,So... frustration meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:22.45,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you borrow the train fee from someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.68,0:05:26.94,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,That is a great proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.73,Default,blonde,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a lovely lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:30.78,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Photo time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:35.80,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... Why are you staring at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't look at me as if\Nyou're expecting something from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.33,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,100 yen, too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:42.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:44.46,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I will not lend something I will not lend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.80,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Can't even let me borrow a mere 100 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:52.11,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the idiot that doesn't even have 100 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.86,Default,blonde,0000,0000,0000,,To be responding with such a frank response to a beautiful shrine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:58.01,Default,blonde,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown up, Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:05:59.21,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.39,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me 100 yen since I'm beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.34,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:08.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I've been pushed around by some threesome group and have absolutely no economic flexibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.57,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.43,0:06:11.91,Default,blonde,0000,0000,0000,,She's directed it at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:12.81,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,100 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:14.72,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,Why even me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:15.62,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,You took a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.68,Default,blonde,0000,0000,0000,,What, that cost money?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.50,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,You want money for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:22.66,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, shrine girls in this city sell their faces, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.56,0:06:25.91,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I am not a shrine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:29.92,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who looks at you, they'll say you're a shrine girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:33.38,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,I am a magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:36.32,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Magician?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.23,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What, just "magician"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:44.12,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just give us something that vague and tell us your specialty, school, magic name, and order name, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:51.82,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if you're going to wear this clothing, at least pretend you're an oriental-style astrologist or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:55.20,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll be that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:07:01.87,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we understand that\Nthis shrine girl is a shrine girl / magician,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.10,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,so just quiet down for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:08.25,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma! Your attitude is completely different from when you dealt with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what she wants to be, then let her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:16.34,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,When I had to prove that magic was real,\Nyou didn't believe me until you stripped me naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:19.52,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,That's major, Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.88,Default,blonde,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these men?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.88,0:07:25.73,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did they...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.54,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,100 yen more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:38.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.45,Default,Himegami,0000,0000,0000,,Cram school teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:42.74,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Cram school... teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:56.64,Default,blue,0000,0000,0000,,But, why does a cram school teacher have to look after a student?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:07.02,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.36,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you said I stripped you naked...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:13.26,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What if they find out we're living together?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:14.32,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:18.79,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,To think that Kamijyo Touma had such bad friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.20,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.49,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,An abandoned cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.07,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma~ Hey~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:30.74,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:34.03,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, I didn't say anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.31,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot have a pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.03,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:40.13,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we take Sphinx home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.67,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,We're not allowed to have pets in student dormitories,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.67,0:08:43.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,so Sphinx can't-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.60,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't give it a name already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.05,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I DON'T CARE!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:51.90,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,WANNA, WANNA, WANNA, WANNA!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:50.94,Default-alt,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:57.65,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you scared it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.65,0:08:58.84,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.71,0:09:00.82,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:05.36,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese samisens are made with cat skin, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.33,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,This country does all these terrible things toward cats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:11.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Your country chases foxes around, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:14.73,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Fox hunting is a traditional and prideful-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:16.40,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:20.59,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The flow of mana around here is being bundled together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.04,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The attribute is earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.49,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,The color is green.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:26.22,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,This formula is a rune?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.19,0:09:28.64,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Index!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.96,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like someone has set up a magic formation around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.08,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,You go home first, Touma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:38.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,She tells me to go home, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:42.99,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.60,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You should know what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:47.19,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,A rune, it's a rune.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:48.45,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,One that removes people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:52.80,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Kamijyo Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:02.99,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Kamijyo Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.81,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:08.79,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a "hi", eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:12.11,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, that's how our relationship should be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:14.42,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Index...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.33,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.59,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,She found a flow of mana and went to investigate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:23.06,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of world was I in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:26.78,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,A daily life where abnormalities like magic surrounded me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.71,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,And, what do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:37.68,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Quit grinning, else I'm gonna have to butcher ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.57,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine Breaker...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.38,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, that's the face I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:59.20,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,That's how our relationship should be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:03.67,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you getting all friendly with me just because we fought on the same side once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:08.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:11.88,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,A lil' secret talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.25,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:24.27,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of Misawa Cram School, the prep school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.27,0:11:25.91,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Misawa Cram School?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:29.41,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,There's a girl being imprisoned there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.72,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Imprisoned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:37.67,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Misawa Cram School has become\Na phony religious cult devoted to science worship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:42.91,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Nevermind what they teach there, the fact is Misawa Cram School has been taken over...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:46.16,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,And this time, by a true and authentic magician...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:50.23,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,No, an alchemist of the Zurich school, to be precise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:51.39,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,True and authentic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:56.06,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know it sounds suspicious; I think so, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.34,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.69,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you a bit too perceptive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:04.09,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:06.75,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If he finds out I lost my memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:13.46,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What, because I just so happen to be listening attentively, you give me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:17.34,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the type of person that likes\Nhis entire conversation to be torn apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.11,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:23.24,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,That the conversation is going smooth isn't a problem either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:28.18,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,The alchemist's name is Aureolus Izzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:30.97,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,He's been hiding for three years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.57,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever he's been doing for these three years...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.39,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,...now, he's back...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:38.69,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:42.40,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's the important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:51.20,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,His target is the girl imprisoned at Misawa Cram School, Deep Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Deep Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:57.48,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,The girl possesses the ability to kill\Na certain organism; that is what he is after.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:00.82,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's that... certain organism?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.21,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,It's been called many things,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:06.98,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,but in simple terms, a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:07.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Vampire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.22,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Do they really exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:16.21,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Not even we, magicians, know the details of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:21.53,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,But, Deep Blood is, in other words, the "power to kill vampires".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:25.09,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,So, we must meet the vampires first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:31.05,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,To do that, don't you think it's a better idea to be in control of Deep Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:33.77,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say, after all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:41.34,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a desperate situation where I have to launch a strike on Misawa Cram School and rescue Deep Blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:46.67,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't nod that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.67,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.15,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you have the right to decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:56.80,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't agree to me, Index will be taken away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.51,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,That's the direction we'll be heading in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:05.46,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,The role that Necessarius has given you is\Na fetter so that Index doesn't betray them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:08.47,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you don't listen,\Nthen you'd be practically useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:12.80,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You're being serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.35,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:17.07,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one making the choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.73,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.98,Default,both,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:37.98,Default-alt,both,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:42.48,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,G-Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.97,0:14:44.43,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:49.47,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, that stomach is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:52.21,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I might've eaten too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:02.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you've grown some splendid ones since the last time I saw you, Index.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:04.14,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a growing girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:08.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.37,0:15:09.90,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you hiding inside your clothes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:11.95,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm not hiding anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.20,0:15:15.33,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of Our Father, in Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.33,0:15:18.14,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,there's no way a sister would lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:23.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So much for your faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.19,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Get that stray cat out of here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:28.98,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Sphinx!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:30.32,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.11,0:15:35.56,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Touma, this clothing is called Walking Church.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.10,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:41.23,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,And a church will open its arms\Nwithout condition to lost sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:44.87,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, Sphinx, who was lost on the streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:47.67,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,is now in the protection of the church, Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:53.37,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,So, you'd be fine with me putting toilet sand into your sleeves?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:57.71,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! I've decided that Sphinx will be protected by the church!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:15:59.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't decide so easily when you haven't thought it through!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.72,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:03.27,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.15,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, you can have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:21.95,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Our Father, in Heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:28.37,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,...your warm light has finally reached\Nthe heartless, cruel, cold-blooded Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.28,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:33.92,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Touma, weren't you going to say something to me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.77,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:39.72,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I seem to have dropped my reference book somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:43.07,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go look for it, so could you stay home and watch over the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.89,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:47.71,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.76,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the cat out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.51,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:58.82,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Sphinx, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:00.35,Default,Index,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy, good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.30,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:14.01,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should leave Innocentius here for her protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:21.67,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,While we're at Misawa Cram School, there's a possibility other magicians might come here and take Index away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:23.43,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,So much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.38,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,You... like Index?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.19,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell are you mentioning that all of a sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:35.80,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's a target to be protected, not a target for romance...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:38.10,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,So, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.59,0:17:40.74,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:53.38,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I thought of Index\Nor how I treated her before I lost my memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:57.70,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice but to desperately keep pretending to be "me".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:00.89,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What can I say... such misfortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:05.29,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It's like there's two of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,This is Misawa Cram School?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.33,0:18:14.14,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem suspicious...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.54,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Suspicious, it doesn't seem...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:22.94,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,However, the building itself is the alchemist's seal, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:24.85,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Is he strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:27.47,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Aureolus Izzard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.11,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,The descendant of the famous Paracelsus...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:33.39,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know of alchemists?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:36.38,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,They can turn lead into gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.59,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,and they can prepare a mixture that gives you immortality?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:41.38,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.77,0:18:47.12,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,But, originally, alchemists had\Nan ultimate objective in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:51.58,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,To model everything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.52,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:58.42,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,If one could bring out whatever he or she imagined in their head into reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:18:59.57,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,what do you think would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.02,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Like, they can bring out anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.95,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we could beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.98,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:10.29,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,You want to stay here and stand guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:17.21,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to help, then confirm\NDeep Blood's face and name right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:18.93,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Here, to be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:22.05,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell the difference between oriental faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:27.99,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Himegami Aisa, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:31.17,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:39.74,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,It seems... unexpectedly normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:41.05,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:44.27,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,On the surface, it's still functioning as a prep school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:48.58,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, what's... that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:53.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,A robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.29,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Is it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:56.11,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:57.82,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:00.12,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's better if we move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:05.87,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it might be a rare sighting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:10.01,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a robot, isn't that something on the science side?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:11.46,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:14.69,Default,Stiyl,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:28.01,Preview,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:27.72,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The ambition of the alchemist,\Nhiding on "the inner face of the coin".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:29.44,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The Thirteen Knights that fight against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.81,0:20:32.56,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,The real objective of the imprisoned Himegami Aisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.84,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Ars Magna".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:37.24,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross paths,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.24,0:20:38.66,Default,Touma,0000,0000,0000,,this epic will begin!
